data_table.description: The subject consent data table contains subject IDs, consent group information, origin of dataset, and subject aliases.

variable.name: CONSENT
variable.description: Consent group as determined by DAC

variable.name: SUBJECT_SOURCE
variable.description: Indicates whether a subject is present in GENEVA study

variable.name: SOURCE_SUBJECT_ID
variable.description: ID of subject for that source, the IDs are the same across this study and Geneva

variable.name: SUBJECT_SOURCE2
variable.description: Repository name for dbGaP study also containing this individual

variable.name: SOURCE_SUBJECT_ID2
variable.description: Subject ID used in the SUBJECT_SOURCE repository
